beer.beer_name: Special Batch: Smoked Mango Chilli Sour
beer.beer_description:
Made exclusively for the Beer Cartel Advent Calendar 2023 this beer is a wild mix of ingredients that come together in complete balance. With subtle Manuka smoke, sweet mango and a slow burning heat this sour is a harmonious blend of flavours. Pairs well with a hot bowl of Laksa.

Malts: Pale, wheat and Manuka smoked
Adjuncts: Mango and Kashmiri chilli
